    <div id="content"><h1>Bulletin Board</h1>
        

<fieldset>
<p>Welcome to the Townsville Community Music Centre bulletin Board.</p> 
<p>The bulletin Board is a free service, intended not only for selling and advertising, but also for any items of news or general interest.</p>
    
<p><strong>Post an item to contribute to the board!</strong> The Music centre is in no way involved with the sale of goods advertised on this page, contributors are responsible for any posts made.</p>

    <a href="post.html"><img src="Images/postbutton.png" alt="Post an ad to the bulletin board"></a>
    </fieldset>

